doc.name: wslegend
doc.description: WSLegend is always used in combination with WSFieldset. It is the title of a fieldset.
doc.parameters: The title comes between the beginning and end tags (see example).
doc.note: wslegend can have all HTML extra's like class, id, etc..
doc.links: Check https://simplegov.wikibase.nl/Special:WSForm for all valid extra attributes
